high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the edge of the large TV cabinet
Pick up the newspaper from the top of the cabinet
Turn right and walk over to the floor lamp by the windows
Turn on the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper under the light of the floor lamp

high_descs: Step forward, turn left and walk to the table.
From the table, pick up the newspaper sitting north of the keys.
Turn around, take a few steps then turn left and walk to the wall, take a right and walk to the window, take a left to the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a newspaper, walk to the lamp, and turn it on.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the black dresser.
Pick up the newspaper that is on the dresser to the right of the television.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the tall abstract lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper in the light of a large abstract lamp.

high_descs: turn left and locate the table
pick up the news paper from the table
turn right and locate the standing light
turn on the standing light
anns.task_desc: turn on the standing light with the newspaper at hand

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black dresser against the wall.
Pick up the newspaper from the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the floor lamp in the corner of the other room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the newspaper on top of the dresser.
Pick up the newspaper from the dresser.
Turn right and walk to the tall lamp in the corner in the other room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the tall lamp in the corner while carrying a newspaper.
